%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20CEO%20of%20edtech%20startup%20Headway%20breaks%20down%20how%20the%20company%20used%20AI%20tools%20to%20improve%20its%20ad%20performance%20by%2040%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headway%20CEO%20Anton%20Pavlovsky%20headshot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d5894e1d8d2deb96b7fc21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHeadway%20CEO%20Anton%20Pavlovsky%3Cp%3EHeadway%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHeadway's%20CEO%20shifted%20to%20an%20AI-focused%20strategy%20after%20a%20Silicon%20Valley%20trip%20in%20April%202023.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20tools%20boosted%20Headway's%20marketing%2C%20achieving%203.3%20billion%20ad%20impressions%20in%20early%202024.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHeadway's%20AI-driven%20ads%20and%20features%20have%20significantly%20increased%20user%20engagement%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20weeks%20after%20OpenAI%20released%20ChatGPT%20to%20the%20public%20in%202022%2C%20Anton%20Pavlovsky%2C%20the%20chief%20executive%20of%20the%20Ukrainian%20edtech%20startup%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmakeheadway.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHeadway%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20wary%20of%20the%20artificial-intelligence%20hype.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20decided%20his%20then-three-year-old%20company%20should%20adopt%20a%20defensive%20strategy%2C%20letting%20other%20companies%20take%20the%20lead%20in%20generative-AI%20investments%2C%20and%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20afterward%2C%20should%20they%20indeed%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20business%20trip%20to%20Silicon%20Valley%20the%20following%20April%20completely%20changed%20Pavlovsky's%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20talked%20with%20so%20many%20very%20smart%20people%20with%20lots%20of%20experience%2C%20and%20those%20people%20said%20that%20this%20is%20definitely%20a%20paradigm%20shift%2C%26quot%3B%20Pavlovsky%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20said%20that%20it's%20akin%20to%20the%20internet%2C%20the%20world%20wide%20web%2C%20then%20the%20smartphone%2C%20and%20then%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20return%2C%20he%20implemented%20a%20companywide%2C%20four-month%2C%20hardcore%20focus%20on%20AI.%20The%20company%20also%20created%20a%20separate%20cross-functional%20team%20to%20help%20integrate%20AI-powered%20features%20into%20its%20various%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPavlovsky%20said%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20tools%20has%20made%20a%20profound%20difference%20to%20the%20company's%20marketing%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20first%20six%20months%20of%202024%2C%20the%20company%20said%20AI-driven%20ads%20reached%203.3%20billion%20impressions.%20The%20company%20said%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20tools%20had%20increased%20the%20return%20on%20investment%20from%20its%20video%20ads%20by%2040%25%20because%20it%20had%20helped%20lower%20the%20costs%20Headway%20would%20have%20previously%20spent%20on%20production.%20Headway%20declined%20to%20disclose%20its%20marketing%20budget%20but%20said%20it%20is%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bmillions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20impact%20is%20on%20opportunity%20costs%20for%20people%2C%20it's%20freeing%20up%20so%20many%20resources%20on%20creative%20and%20more%20value-add%20endeavors%20for%20experimenting%20with%20crazy%20ideas%2C%26quot%3B%20Pavlovsky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeadway%20joins%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20marketers%20looking%20to%20harness%20AI%20tools%2C%20in%20part%20to%20reduce%20their%20advertising%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20buy-now-pay-later%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fklarna-ceo-comments-ai-smaller-marketing-team-produce-more-savings-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKlarna%20made%20waves%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20it%20said%20AI%20had%20helped%20cut%20its%20spend%20on%20marketing%20agencies%20by%2025%25.%20A%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gartner.com%2Fen%2Fmarketing%2Ftopics%2Fai-in-marketing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGartner%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20predicted%20that%2030%25%20of%20outbound%20marketing%20messages%20from%20large%20companies%20would%20be%20synthetically%20generated%20by%202025.%20The%20rapid%20adoption%20of%20the%20tools%20has%20the%20marketing%20industry%20excited%20about%20AI's%20prospects%2C%20but%20some%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-is-set-to-dominate-cannes-lions-ad-festival-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euneasy%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20consequences%20for%20agency%20jobs%20and%20question%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-has-marketing-problem-people-dont-like-hearing-about-it-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhether%20consumers%20are%20ready%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20an%20influx%20of%20ads%20using%20or%20mentioning%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225283ce02-8cac-4410-a913-fe59c246f13c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeadway%20is%20using%20AI%20tools%20like%20HeyGen%2C%20Rask%2C%20and%20Midjourney%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%20Ukraine%20in%202019%2C%20Headway%20operates%20a%20portfolio%20of%20educational%20apps%20that%20combined%20have%20been%20downloaded%20by%20more%20than%20110%20million%20users%20worldwide.%20The%20company%20continues%20to%20be%20headquartered%20in%20Ukraine's%20capital%2C%20Kyiv%2C%20though%20most%20of%20its%20users%20are%20based%20in%20the%20US.%20(The%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D1018097949135255%26id%3D250289965916061%26set%3Da.351463732465350%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20it%20had%20helped%20the%20majority%20of%20its%20staff%20and%20families%20who%20wanted%20to%20move%20away%20from%20the%20country%20to%20do%20so%2C%20though%20some%20have%20since%20returned.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20flagship%20app%2C%20Headway%2C%20offers%2015-minute%20summaries%20of%20popular%20nonfiction%20books%2C%20as%20well%20as%20challenges%20and%20daily%20micro-learning%20sessions.%20Other%20apps%20in%20its%20portfolio%20include%20the%20brain-training%20app%20Impulse%2C%20the%20AddMile%20coaching%20platform%2C%20and%20its%20newest%2C%20Skillsta%2C%20which%20is%20a%20training%20app%20for%20soft%20skills%20like%20critical%20thinking%20and%20empathy.%20The%20company%20makes%20money%20through%20paid%20subscriptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeadway%20has%20leaned%20heavily%20on%20advertising%20on%20digital%20platforms%20like%20Meta's%20Instagram%20and%20Facebook%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20TikTok%20in%20order%20to%20grow%20its%20user%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20Headway's%20user-generated-content%20video%20ads%20are%20now%20produced%20using%20some%20element%20of%20AI%20technology%2C%20such%20as%20for%20subtitles%20or%20voiceovers%2C%20the%20company%20said.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-money-from-ugc-user-generated-content-ads%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUGC%20ads%3C%2Fa%3E%20refer%20to%20those%20that%20blend%20in%20with%20other%20content%20on%20an%20app%2C%20such%20as%20vertical%20video%20ads%20on%20TikTok%20and%20YouTube%20Shorts%2C%20and%20are%20often%20produced%20by%20creators%20rather%20than%20professional%20production%20teams.%20These%20ads%20account%20for%2030%25%20to%2050%25%20of%20the%20purchases%20of%20Headway%20subscriptions%20or%20signups%20to%20its%207-day%20free%20trials%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Headway%20used%20to%20rely%20heavily%20on%20stock%20images%20for%20its%20static%20ads%2C%20around%20one%20in%20five%20of%20its%20paid%20downloads%20or%20trials%20are%20now%20driven%20by%20static%20ads%20that%20use%20AI-generated%20images%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FgXGw3NIf3k4%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Nibble%3A%20Replace%20Scrolling%20Addiction%20With%20Art%20Learning%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20company%20launched%20the%20French%20version%20of%20its%20Headway%20app%2C%20it%20used%20the%20AI%20tools%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rask.ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERask%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.heygen.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHeyGen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deepl.com%2Fen%2Fwrite%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeepL%3C%2Fa%3E%20translator%2C%20to%20translate%20a%20video%20ad%20featuring%20an%20English-speaking%20creator%20into%20a%20convincing%20ad%20for%20a%20French%20audience%20using%20AI%20voiceover%20and%20lipsync%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FgXGw3NIf3k4%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Nibble%3A%20Replace%20Scrolling%20Addiction%20With%20Art%20Learning%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EElsewhere%2C%20Headway%20used%20tools%2C%20including%20HeyGen%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.d-id.com%2Fphoto-to-video%2F%3Futm_term%3Dbrand-ad%26utm_term%3Dd-id%2520ai%26utm_term%3Dd-id%2520ai%26utm_campaign%3Dbrand-eu%26utm_source%3Dadwords%26utm_medium%3Dppc%26utm_content%3D611130303518%26hsa_acc%3D6149207258%26hsa_cam%3D17780208183%26hsa_grp%3D141566902480%2