er.com%2F6690f9c39caa6ed01e00fefb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20said%20xAI%20has%20brought%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20powerful%20AI%20training%20system%20in%20the%20world%26quot%3B%20online.%20%3Cp%3EMarc%20Piasecki%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElon%20Musk%20just%20put%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20Nvidia%20chips%20to%20work.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20on%20Monday%20his%20company%2C%20xAI%2C%20brought%20its%20AI%20training%20cluster%2C%20Colossus%2C%20online.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBuilt%20with%20Nvidia's%20H100%20GPUs%2C%20the%20cluster%20could%20help%20Musk%20play%20catch%20up%20to%20Meta.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20might%20be%20distracted%20right%20now%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrazil-starlink-sanctions-amid-feud-elon-musk-x-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrazil's%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20its%20decision%20to%20ban%20X%2C%20but%20he%20isn't%20letting%20that%20stop%20him%20from%20pushing%20forwards%20with%20his%20AI%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20billionaire%20said%20xAI%20%E2%80%94%20the%20company%20he%20launched%20in%20July%202023%20%E2%80%94%20had%20brought%20a%20massive%20new%20training%20cluster%20of%20chips%20online%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20claiming%20it%20represented%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20powerful%20AI%20training%20system%20in%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20system%2C%20dubbed%20%26quot%3BColossus%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20built%20at%20a%20site%20in%20Memphis%20using%20100%2C000%20chips%20from%20Nvidia%2C%20specifically%20its%20H100%20GPUs.%20According%20to%20Musk%2C%20the%20current%20cluster%20was%20built%20within%20122%20days%20and%20will%20%26quot%3Bdouble%20in%20size%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20few%20months%20as%20more%20GPUs%20a