t%20has%20made%20it%20impossible%20for%20her%20to%20train%20the%20usual%20hours.%20The%2034-year-old%20former%20world%20No.1%2C%20who%20was%20the%20first%20Indian%20shuttler%20to%20win%20an%20Olympic%20medal%20with%20her%20bronze%20in%20London%202012%2C%20participated%20in%20three%20editions%20of%20the%20Games%20before%20being%20hampered%20by%20injuries.%20The%202010%20and%202018%20Commonwealth%20Games%20gold-medallist%20said%20she%20can%20no%20longer%20overlook%20the%20fact%20that%20her%20career%20is%20in%20its%20final%20leg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20knee%20is%20not%20very%20good.%20I%20have%20arthritis.%20My%20cartilage%20has%20gone%20to%20a%20bad%20state.%20It%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20push%20for%20eight-nine%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20Nehwal%20said%20on%20the%20'House%20of%20Glory'%20podcast%20hosted%20by%20shooting%20great%20Gagan%20Narang%2C%20who%20was%20India's%20chef-de-mission%20in%20the%20recent%20Paris%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20will%20you%20challenge%20the%20best%20players%20in%20the%20world%20in%20such%20a%20state%3F%20I%20think%20I%20will%20have%20to%20accept%20it%20somewhere.%20Because%20two%20hours%20of%20training%20is%20not%20good%20enough%20to%20play%20with%20the%20highest%20level%20of%20players%20and%20get%20the%20desired%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehwal%20said%20she%20is%20still%20considering%20the%20impact%20retirement%20will%20have%20on%20her%20but%20admitted%20that%20she%20would%20eventually%20have%20to%20take%20a%20call.%20The%20trailblazing%20star%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20BJP%20member%20now%2C%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20action%20more%20than%20a%20year%20ago%20in%20the%20Singapore%20Open%20where%20she%20lost%20in%20the%20opening%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20also%20thinking%20about%20it%20(retirement).%20It%20will%20be%20sad%20because%20it%20is%20like%20a%20job%20that%20a%20normal%20person%20does.%20Obviously%2C%20a%20sportsperson's%20career%20is%20always%20a%20short%20one.%20I%20started%20at%20the%20age%20of%209.%20I%20will%20be%2035%20next%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20also%20had%20a%20long%20career%20and%20I%20am%20very%20proud%20of%20that.%20I%20have%20broken%20my%20body%20to%20a%20great%20extent.%20I%20am%20happy%20with%20what%20I%20have%20done%20and%20given%20it%20all.%20(I)%20will%20assess%20how%20I%20feel%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Padma%20Shri%20awardee%20said%20competing%20at%20the%20Olympics%20was%20her%20childhood%20dream%20and%20missing%20the%20showpiece%20for%20two%20consecutive%20editions%20has%20been%20hurtful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompeting%20at%20the%20Olympics%20is%20a%20childhood%20dream%20for%20all.%20You%20prepare%20to%20reach%20that%20level%20for%20years.%20Hence%2C%20at%20times%2C%20when%20you%20realise%20you%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20make%20it%2C%20it%20hurts%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20expressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20it%20is%20not%20like%20you%20do%20not%20want%20to%20play%2C%20but%20your%20body%20is%20telling%20that%20you%20are%20not%20doing%20well%20and%20you%20have%20injuries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehwal%2C%20however%2C%20said%20she%20would%20look%20back%20at%20her%20run%20in%20the%20Games%20with%20pride.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20have%20done%20a%20lot%20of%20hard%20work.%20I%20competed%20in%20three%20Olympics.%20I%20gave%20my%20100%20per%20cent%20in%20all%20of%20them.%20I%20can%20take%20pride%20in%20that%20and%20be%20happy%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehwal%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20pressure%20of%20expectations%20and%20said%20as%20a%20top%20athlete%2C%20she%20has%20faced%20it%20not%20just%20from%20observers%20of%20the%20game%20but%20also%20from%20near%20and%20dear%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20become%20a%20big%20player%2C%20your%20friends%2C%20family%2C%20coaches%2C%20sponsors%2C%20everyone%20wants%20you%20to%20perform.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20stakeholders%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20already%20a%20short%20career%20span%2C%20athletes%20cannot%20afford%20to%20take%20a%20four-year%20break%20and%20have%20to%20keep%20performing%20continuously.%20If%20you%20wish%20to%20become%20an%20international%20champion%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20strong%20to%20make%20tough%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725366660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-10%2Foucjqsto_saina-sindhu-afp_625x300_08_October_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fbadminton%2Findian-olympic-badminton-great-to-retire-due-to-arthritis-player-says-cartilage-has-gone-6481671%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%202010%20and%202018%20Commonwealth%20Games%20gold-medallist%20said%20she%20can%20no%20longer%20overlook%20the%20fact%20that%20her%20career%20is%20in%20its%20final%20leg.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fbadminton%2Findian-olympic-badminton-great-to-retire-due-to-arthritis-player-says-cartilage-has-gone-6481671%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Before%20people%20rush%20to%20Montreal%20to%20live%20their%20best%20life%2C%20they%20should%20know%20my%20city's%20beautiful%20veneer%20is%20starting%20to%20crack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20Montreal%20with%20vignetting%20around%20the%20edges%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a01e5b2d66759f66fd9107%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMontreal%20is%20often%20praised%20for%20its%20low%20cost%20of%20living%20and%20high%20quality%20of%20life%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20the%20whole%20story.%3Cp%3EiStock%3B%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMontreal's%20low%20cost%20of%20living%20and%20high%20quality%20of%20life%20have%20made%20it%20a%20hot%20spot%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20the%20city%20has%20been%20dealing%20with%20a%20housing%20shortage%2C%20making%20it%20hard%20to%20move%20here.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFrench-language%20laws%20and%20endless%20construction%20have%20also%20made%20it%20harder%20for%20businesses%20to%20thrive.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20newsfeed%20seemingly%20tells%20me%20to%20move%20to%20a%20different%20city%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20lists%20and%20rankings%20of%20the%20best%20places%20to%20live%20are%20fun%20to%20scan%20through%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20I%20%3Cem%3Ewould%3C%2Fem%3E%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-finland-is-the-happiest-country-former-international-student-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehappier%20in%20Finland%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20but%20seeing%20my%20own%20city%20make%20a%20list%20gave%20me%20pause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmontreal-canada-city-low-cost-of-living-quality-of-life-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMercer's%20annual%20cost-of-living%20report%20for%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Montreal%20has%20a%20low%20cost%20of%20living%20and%20a%20high%20quality%20of%20life.%20Of%20the%20226%20global%20cities%20the%20report%20compared%2C%20only%20eight%20fell%20into%20the%20honorable%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMontreal%20is%20a%20gem%20of%20a%20city%3A%20It's%20safe%20and%20walkable%2C%20with%20a%20vibrant%20nightlife%20and%20a%20cultural%20calendar%20packed%20with%20events.%20It's%20also%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatistique.quebec.ca%2Fen%2Fcommunique%2Fcroissance-demographique-record-moitie-regions-quebec%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efastest-growing%20cities%20in%20Canada%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20why%20wouldn't%20you%20want%20to%20get%20in%20on%20the%20action%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20lived%20here%20with%20my%20family%20for%20over%2050%20years%20and%20relish%20ambling%20through%20the%20different%20boroughs%2C%20each%20with%20its%20distinctive%20history%2C%20charm%2C%20architecture%2C%20and%20culinary%20delights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20notion%20of%20a%20magical%2C%20miracle%20city%20%26quot%3Beveryone%20should%20move%20to%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20mirage%20%E2%80%94%20no%20matter%20how%20many%20%26quot%3Bbest%20places%20to%20live%26quot%3B%20listicles%20we%20end%20up%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2208425bc8-f0c0-4ec4-9085-983f7d2cea97%5C%22%3EFinding%20housing%20in%20the%20Canadian%20city%20can%20be%20incredibly%20difficult%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20we're%20known%20for%20our%20quaint%20cobblestone%20streets%2C%20Montreal%20is%20far%20from%20a%20fairy%20tale%20for%20some%20renters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMontreal%20native%20Lisette%20Jemmott%20knows%20too%20well%20how%20difficult%20navigating%20the%20market%20can%20be.%20At%2026%2C%20she%20returned%20to%20the%20city%20after%20living%20in%20Toronto%20for%2010%20years%2C%20longing%20for%20the%20high%20quality%20of%20life%20and%20phenomenal%20food%20scene%20she%20remembered%20from%20her%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2039%2C%20Jemmott%20is%20looking%20to%20upgrade%20after%20living%20in%20a%20basic%20two-bedroom%20apartment%20without%20included%20amenities%20and%20utilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20she%20has%20a%20steady%20job%20in%20event%20planning%20and%20marketing%20that%20pays%20market%20value%2C%20all%20the%20new%20apartment%20listings%20she%20found%20were%20too%20expensive%20for%20her%20budget%20of%201%2C500%20CAD%2C%20or%20about%20%241%2C112%20a%20month.%20Worse%20yet%2C%20rental%20prices%20seemed%20to%20jump%20by%20at%20least%2050%20CAD%20every%20time%20she%20searched.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221792%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22pool%20in%20a%20modern%20luxury%20apartment%20building%20in%20montreal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccae891aa2ac29ee34299f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221344%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApartment%20prices%20have%20jumped%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20especially%20in%20luxury%20buildings.%20%3Cp%3EAnatoli%20Igolkin%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20provincial%20protections%20that%20limit%20and%20regulate%20rent%20increases%20for%20existing%20leases%2C%20Jemmott's%20monthly%20payment%20has%20only%20gone%20from%20900%20to%201%2C100%20CAD%20over%20the%20last%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20similar%20units%20in%20her%20building%20now%20cost%201%2C500%20to%201%2C700%20CAD%20a%20month%2C%20and%20things%20only%20seem%20to%20worsen%20for%20new%20renters.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frclalq.qc.ca%2Fpublications%2Fdemenager-un-cauchemar-pour-les-locataires%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Coalition%20of%20Housing%20Committees%20and%20Tenants%20Associations%20of%20Quebec%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Montreal%20rental%20prices%20have%20increased%20by%20an%20average%20of%2027%25%20between%202020%20and%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20Jemmott%20decided%20she%20was%20willing%20to%20downsize%20from%20a%20two-bedroom%20to%20a%20one-bedroom%20apartment%20to%20live%20in%20a%20building%20with%20more%20amenities%2C%20her%20search%20ended%20in%20vain.%20For%20now%2C%20she's%20staying%20put.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Falduto%2C%20a%20ReMax%20real-estate%20broker%20who%20serves%20Montreal%20and%20its%20surrounding%20suburbs%2C%20isn't%20surprised%20by%20Jemmott's%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20renters%20could%20secure%20a%20%26quot%3Bluxury%20condo%20in%20a%20big%20complex%20with%20a%20pool%20and%20all%20kinds%20of%20amenities%26quot%3B%20for%201%2C500%20CAD%20a%20month.%20Now%2C%20renters%20are%20getting%20%26quot%3Ba%20standard%20two-bedroom%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20same%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20broker%20added%20that%20when%20one%20of%20those%20%26quot%3Bunicorn%26quot%3B%20affordable%20luxury%20apartments%20comes%20on%20the%20market%20in%20Montreal%2C%20he's%20inundated%20with%2010%20to%2015%20tour%20requests%20almost%20instantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221781%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20row%20of%20colorful%20apartments%20in%20montreal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccaf45c72ebc54a40ed03e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221336%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20has%20become%20harder%20for%20Montreal%20renters%20to%20check%20everything%20off%20their%20wish%20lists%20without%20raising%20budgets.%3Cp%3ECatherine%20Zibo%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Jemmott%20is%20keeping%20her%20fingers%20crossed%20that%20home%20prices%20fall%20next%20year%2C%20so%20she%20might%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20buy.%20But%20Falduto%20noted%20a%20troubling%20new%20trend%20for%20first-time%20homebuyers%3A%20Starter%20homes%20in%20Montreal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nesto.ca%2Fmortgage-basics%2Fquebec-housing-market-outlook%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecost%20at%20least%2040%25%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20they%20did%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20buyers%20qualify%20for%20a%20mortgage%2C%20the%20broker%20said%20it's%20often%20not%20enough%20for%20them%20to%20close%20a%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20people%20who%20would%20otherwise%20buy%20stay%20in%20rental%20properties%20longer%2C%20leaving%20fewer%20units%20available%20for%20the%20next%20wave%20of%20renters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20rented%20in%20the%20city%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20before%20we%20bought%20our%20starter%20home%20in%20the%20late%201990s.%20But%20back%20then%2C%20it%20was%20a%20buyers'%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20condition%20of%20Montreal's%20housing%20market%2C%20our%20%26quot%3Bstarter%26quot%3B%20is%20now%20just%20our%20forever%20home.%20It's%20made%20more%20sense%20for%20us%20to%20renovate%20instead%20of%20trying%20to%20find%20something%20bigger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217085ce8-6c63-4621-b3f8-c4959fb6b9a2%5C%22%3ERising%20rent%20prices%20aren't%20the%20only%20thing%20making%20it%20harder%20for%20young%20professionals%20to%20stick%20around%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20city%20of%201.8%20million%2C%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtl.org%2Fen%2Fexperience%2Ftop-student-city%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enearly%20200%2C000%20students%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20about%2011%25%20of%20the%20population%20%E2%80%94%20largely%20because%20of%20top-notch%20schools%20like%20McGill%2C%20Concordia%2C%20and%20Universit%C3%A9%20de%20Montr%C3%A9al.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20local%20business%20developer%20Glenn%20Castanheira%20said%20Montreal%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20fly%20trap%20for%20bright-eyed%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20the%20perfect%20ingredients%20to%20attract%20that%20talent%20because%20of%20quality%20of%20life%20and%20higher%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2020%25%20of%20those%20aforementioned%20students%20are%20international%2C%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20affordable%20rentals%20makes%20it%20more%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20stick%20around%20after%20school.%20What%20should%20be%20a%20vast%2C%20diverse%20talent%20pool%20becomes%20more%20of%20a%20puddle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20do%20stick%20around%20require%20higher%20starting%20salaries%20to%20cover%20their%20rent%2C%20which%20only%20drives%20up%20business%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221776%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22concordia%20university%20in%20montreal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccafff1aa2ac29ee342b22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221332%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EConcordia%20is%20one%20of%20Montreal's%20big%20universities.%20%3Cp%3EEQRoy%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20if%20young%20professionals%20don't%20speak%20French%2C%20there%20isn't%20a%20lot%20of%20incentive%20for%20them%20to%20stay%20and%20strengthen%20the%20Quebec%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Fmontreal%2Fquebecs-new-french-language-rules-1.7247020%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Quebec%2520government%2520will%2520go%2Cin%2520French%2520by%2520June%25202025.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elanguage%20signage%20laws%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Quebec%2C%20which%20will%20come%20into%20effect%20in%20June%202025%2C%20state%20that%20businesses%20must%20give%20French%20at%20least%20twice%20as%20much%20space%20on%20their%20storefronts%20as%20any%20other%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221787%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22french%20signs%20on%20a%20storefront%20in%20montreal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccb1af43b5e59d16b5290c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221340%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStores%20will%20be%20required%20to%20have%20French%20signage%20in%20Montreal.%20%3Cp%3EMarc%20Bruxelle%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EErkan%20Y%C3%B6nder%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20real%20estate%20and%20finance%20at%20Concordia%20University%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20he's%20seen%20new%20graduates%20get%20driven%20away%20by%20this%20pressure%20to%20be%20bilingual.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Montreal%20native%2C%20I%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20home%20where%20four%20languages%20(sometimes%20more)%20could%20be%20heard%20throughout%20the%20day.%20I%20thought%20this%20was%20the%20norm%20for%20everyone.%20The%20city's%20language%20rules%20may%20send%20the%20wrong%20message%20to%20foreign%20students%20who%20want%20to%20make%20Montreal%20their%20home%20but%20aren't%20native%20French%20speakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLearning%20a%20new%20language%20shouldn't%20be%20a%20threat%20or%20a%20burden%2C%26quot%3B%20Y%C3%B6nder%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20are%20better%20ways%20to%20motivate%20young%20kids%20to%20learn%20French%20and%20to%20integrate%20French%20into%20their%20lives%20rather%20than%20harsh%20policies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e47199b6-29bc-463a-b720-0954364270ec%5C%22%3EPeople%20can%20come%20here%20looking%20for%20joie%20de%20vivre%2C%20but%20they'll%20run%20into%20some%20roadblocks%20%E2%80%94%20literally%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221781%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22construction%20signs%20on%20a%20street%20in%20Montreal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccb2451aa2ac29ee342d3c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221336%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEven%20the%20construction%20signs%20are%20in%20French.%20%3Cp%3EChristopher%20O'Donnell%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBusinesses%20also%20have%20to%20compete%20against%20the%20city's%20carousel%20of%20construction%20projects%2C%20which%20can%20reduce%20foot%20traffic%2C%20among%20other%20issues.%20After%20all%2C%20at%20382%20years%20old%2C%20Montreal%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20upkeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmontreal.ca%2Fen%2Farticles%2Fwhy-does-montreal-carry-out-so-many-construction-projects-each-year-15663%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECity%20of%20Montreal%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmontreal.ca%2Fen%2Farticles%2Fwhy-does-montreal-carry-out-so-many-construction-projects-each-year-15663%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E500%20construction%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20carried%20out%20within%20the%20territory%20annually%2C%20which%20is%20why%20locals%20quip%20that%20Montreal%20has%20two%20seasons%3A%20winter%20and%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20even%20a%20joke%20when%20I%20say%20even%20if%20the%20city%20opens%20up%20a%206-inch%20hole%20in%20the%20pavement%2C%20something%20like%2012%20cones%20appear%20all%2