20some%20serious%20flaws%20in%20research%2C%20which%20my%20co-founders%20and%20I%20hope%20to%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2256427b86-86f6-4a4e-9c26-73ed376dd990%5C%22%3EI%20brought%20my%20baby%20to%20an%20accelerator%20when%20he%20was%203%20weeks%20old%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20personal%20and%20professional%20support%2C%20I've%20kept%20my%20career%20on%20track%20even%20while%20growing%20our%20family.%20When%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbreast-cancer-pregnancy-baby-diagnosis-birth-chemotherapy-2022-09%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeight%20months%20pregnant%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20discovered%20that%20Besample%20was%20accepted%20to%20Techstars%2C%20a%20three-month%2C%20in-person%20accelerator.%20My%20husband%20said%20he%20could%20care%20for%20the%20three%20older%20kids%20while%20I%20took%20the%20baby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20showed%20up%20with%20my%20son%20Darwin%20when%20he%20was%20just%20three%20weeks%20old.%20Techstars%20was%20nothing%20but%20supportive.%20They%20asked%20if%20I%20needed%20space%20to%20nurse%20Darwin%20or%20put%20him%20down%20for%20a%20nap.%20During%20the%20demo%20night%2C%20which%20comes%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20accelerator%2C%20they%20celebrated%20Darwin%20as%20the%20youngest%20Techstars%20resident%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20through%20Techstars%20that%20I%20got%20tickets%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fy-combinator-founder-says-sam-altman-was-not-fired-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EY%20Combinator%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Female%20Founders%20Conference.%20Y%20Combinator%20is%20a%20big%20deal%20in%20the%20startup%20world%2C%20and%20I%20was%20eager%20to%20be%20inspired%20by%20other%20female%20founders.%20I%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Felena-brandt%2Frecent-activity%2Fall%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20posted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20once-in-a-lifetime%20opportunity%20and%20wondered%20in%20the%20same%20post%20whether%20Darwin%20would%20make%20any%20baby%20friends.%20I%20expected%20babies%20would%20not%20only%20be%20welcomed%20but%20celebrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20wasn't%20the%20case%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222963cc86-cba3-4b60-b21a-846a93712505%5C%22%3EI%20was%20asked%20to%20leave%20during%20a%20talk%20about%20growing%20a%20company%20while%20having%20an%20infant%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20away%2C%20I%20noticed%20no%20other%20babies.%20Then%2C%20I%20listened%20to%20Tracy%20Young%2C%20a%20mom%20and%20founder%2C%20talk%20about%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-running-business-tips-work-life-balance-find-time-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emothering%20experience%20while%20starting%20a%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20discussed%20pumping%20before%20investment%20meetings%20and%20the%20other%20very%20physical%2C%20biological%20challenges%20of%20being%20a%20founder%20with%20an%20infant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDarwin%20was%20in%20a%20stroller%2C%20and%20I%20was%20rocking%20him%20back%20and%20forth%20to%20sleep.%20When%20he%20started%20babbling%20and%20cooing%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20the%20back%20of%20the%20room.%20That's%20when%20someone%20approached%20me%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWould%20you%20like%20to%20stroll%20your%20baby%20outside%3F%20I%20want%20people%20to%20get%20the%20full%20experience%20out%20of%20this%20conference.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20later%20learned%20she%20was%20one%20of%20the%20partners%20of%20Y%20Combinator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226e35f24b-aa5c-45fe-9fc6-915e6cc18f99%5C%22%3EThere's%20a%20tension%20in%20business%20about%20whether%20there's%20room%20for%20families%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20naming%20this%20woman%20because%20I%20think%20the%20problem%20is%20bigger%20than%20me%20or%20her.%20It's%20about%20this%20tension%20in%20the%20business%20world%20right%20now.%20To%20many%20people%2C%20including%20me%2C%20the%20pandemic%20showed%2