ress%20may%20be%20looking%20to%20forge%20an%20alliance%2C%20provided%20the%20state%20leadership%20plays%20ball.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20The%20AAP%20View%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20AAP%20leader%20and%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20has%20welcomed%20reports%20that%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20asked%20leaders%20to%20explore%20the%20option%20of%20an%20alliance%20with%20AAP.%20He%20said%20a%20final%20call%20on%20this%20will%20be%20taken%20after%20consulting%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20in%20jail%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20welcome%20it.%20Our%20priority%20is%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP...%20Our%20Haryana%20in-charge%20Sandeep%20Pathak%20and%20Sushil%20Gupta%20will%20discuss%20it%20and%20take%20a%20final%20decision%20and%20inform%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20about%20it%20and%20a%20decision%20will%20be%20taken%20accordingly...%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20AAP%20will%20contest%20all%2090%20seats%20in%20Haryana%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHard%20Bargaining%20Likely%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20had%20tied%20up%20for%20the%2010%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Haryana%20and%20the%20Chandigarh%20parliamentary%20seat.%20While%20the%20Congress%20won%20five%20seats%20in%20Haryana%20and%20the%20Chandigarh%20seat%20too%2C%20AAP%20did%20not%20benefit%20much%20from%20the%20alliance.%20Shortly%20after%20the%20poll%20results%2C%20a%20section%20of%20AAP's%20Haryana%20leaders%20blamed%20the%20Congress%20for%20the%20defeat%20of%20its%20candidate%20Sushil%20Gupta%20in%20Haryana's%20Kurukshetra.%20Against%20this%20backdrop%2C%20any%20alliance%20talk%20between%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20for%20the%20upcoming%20election%20is%20likely%20to%20see%20hard%20bargaining%20from%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725363600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fi5p7