%20representation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20massive%20row%20had%20erupted%20over%20the%20Netflix%20drama%2C%20which%20tells%20the%20story%20of%20the%20hijack%20of%20Indian%20Airlines%20flight%20IC-814%20by%20Pakistan-based%20terror%20outfit%20Harkat-ul-Mujahideen%20in%201999.%20Five%20hijackers%20took%20control%20of%20the%20plane%20and%20diverted%20it%20to%20Afghanistan%2C%20which%20was%20then%20ruled%20by%20the%20Taliban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20then%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20released%20three%20terrorists%20-%20Masood%20Azhar%2C%20Ahmed%20Omar%20Saeed%20Sheikh%20and%20Mushtaq%20Zargar%20-%20to%20secure%20the%20release%20of%20154%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'Bhola'%2C%20'Shankar'%20Row%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20series%20was%20published%20hundreds%20of%20social%20media%20users%20accused%20the%20creators%20-%20Anubhav%20Sinha%20and%20Trishant%20Srivastava%20-%20of%20changing%20the%20names%20of%20two%20hijackers%20to%20'Bhola'%20and%20'Shankar'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20been%20claimed%20as%20distortion%20of%20historical%20facts%20and%20critics%20have%20declared%20it%20misrepresents%20the%20terrorists'%20real%20identities.%20They%20have%20also%20claimed%20it%2C%20therefore%2C%20offends%20Hindu%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnobody-has-right-to-why-netflix-content-chief-was-summoned-over-ic-814-6473142%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BNobody%20Has%20Right%20To...%26quot%3B%3A%20Why%20Netflix%20Content%20Chief%20Was%20Summoned%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20January%202000%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20had%20revealed%20the%20real%20names%20of%20the%20five%20hijackers%20-%20Ibrahim%20Athar%2C%20Shahid%20Akhtar%20Sayed%2C%20Sunny%20Ahmed%20Qazi%2C%20Mistri%20Zahoor%20Ibrahim%20and%20Shakir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20m