%20October.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20will%20now%20cost%20about%20%2462%2C%20though%20Australians%20and%20some%20Pacific%20Islanders%20are%20exempt.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20fee%20increase%20seeks%20to%20address%20tourism%20and%20conservation%20challenges%20from%20rising%20visitor%20numbers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-zealand-best-ways-to-save-money-travel-tips-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20Zealand%3C%2Fa%3E's%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mbie.govt.nz%2Fimmigration-and-tourism%2Ftourism%2Ftourism-funding%2Finternational-visitor-conservation-and-tourism-levy%2Fwhat-is-the-ivl%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520IVL%2520is%2520a%2520%252435%2Celigible%2520visitor%2520to%2520New%2520Zealand.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%20on%20Tuesday%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20will%20triple%20entry%20fees%20for%20foreign%20tourists%20starting%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Visitor%20Conservation%20and%20Tourism%20Levy%20(IVL)%20for%20foreign%20tourists%20will%20increase%20from%20the%20current%20fee%20of%20NZD%2035%20(about%20%2422%20in%20US%20currency)%20to%20NZD%20100%20(about%20%2462%20in%20American%20money).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mbie.govt.nz%2Fimmigration-and-tourism%2Ftourism%2Ftourism-funding%2Finternational-visitor-conservation-and-tourism-levy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20New%20Zealand's%20Ministry%20of%20Business%2C%20Innovation%2C%20and%20Employment%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethe%20IVL%20exists%20to%20%26quot%3Baddress%20current%20challenges%20in%20the%20tourism%20and%20conservation%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20ensuring%20that%20New%20Zealanders%20do%20not%20%26quot%3Bunduly%20bear%26quot%3B%20the%20costs%20associated%20with%20international%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20noted%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-zealand-adds-jobs-residency-fast-track-immigration-green-list-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20Zealand%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20experienced%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20international%20visitors%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20which%20it%20said%20has%20challenged%20the%20country's%20%26quot%3Binfrastructure%2C%20environment%2C%20communities%2C%20and%20the%20social%20license%20for%20tourism%20to%20operate%20in%20certain%20areas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAustralian%20citizens%2C%20people%20from%20certain%20Pacific%20Island%20nations%2C%20and%20those%20transiting%20through%20New%20Zealand%20are%20exempt%20from%20the%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IVL%20has%20been%20used%20to%20fund%20various%20tourism%20and%20conservation%20initiatives%2C%20including%20pest%20control%2C%20biodiversity%20investments%2C%20and%20enhancing%20visitor%20access%20to%20tourism%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mbie.govt.nz%2Fdmsdocument%2F28322-proposed-changes-to-the-international-visitor-conservation-and-tourism-levy-ivl%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsultation%20held%20in%20June%20on%20proposed%20changes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20included%201%2C100%20submissions%2C%20found%20that%2088%25%20of%20submitters%20agreed%20that%20the%20current%20level%20of%20IVL%20revenue%20%E2%80%94%20about%20%2450%20million%20US%20%E2%80%94%20was%20insufficient%20to%20address%20issues%20facing%20tourism%20and%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%2093%25%20of%20submitters%20agreed%20that%20the%20IVL%20fee%20should%20be%20increased%2C%20with%20a%20majority%20favoring%20the%20biggest%20price%20increase%20to%20NZD%20100.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mbie.govt.nz%2Fimmigration-and-tourism%2Ftourism%2Ftourism-funding%2Finternational-visitor-conservation-and-tourism-levy%2Fwhat-is-the-ivl%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520IVL%2520is%2520a%2520%252435%2Celigible%2520visitor%2520to%2520New%2520Zealand.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Ministry%20of%20Business%2C%20Innovation%2C%20and%20Employment%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fa%3Eincreased%20IVL%20amount%20is%20expected%20to%20generate%20about%20%24229%20million%20in%20New%20Zealand%20currency%20yearly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20study%20published%20by%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tourismnewzealand.com%2Fassets%2Finsights%2Findustry-insights%2FViews-on-Tourism-New-Zealand-YE-Dec-23-EXTERNAL.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Tourism%20New%20Zealand%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20found%20that%20New%20Zealand%20residents%20felt%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarcelona-overtourism-making-it-impossible-to-live-there-local-says-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etourism%3C%2Fa%3E%20negatively%20impacted%20their%20communities%20through%20increased%20litter%2C%20difficulty%20finding%20parking%2C%20and%20heavier%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20two-thirds%20of%20those%20surveyed%20also%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20tourism%20on%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.royalsociety.org.nz%2Fassets%2F109-Alpha-Series-Tourism-and-the-environment.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Royal%20Society%20of%20New%20Zealand%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20independent%20non-profit%20that%20provides%20funding%20and%20policy%20advice%20on%20the%20region's%20science%20and%20technology%2C%20an%20influx%20of%20tourists%20can%20lead%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpopular-travel-destinations-fight-overtourism-unique-strategies-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eovercrowding%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehabitat%20destruction%2C%20wildlife%20disturbance%2C%20and%20noise%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20tourism%20contributes%20to%203.7%25%20of%20New%20Zealand's%20economy%2C%20forming%20one%20of%20its%20main%20industries%2C%20it%20also%20directly%20impacts%20the%20country's%20natural%20landmarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20country's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.doc.govt.nz%2Fglobalassets%2Fdocuments%2Fconservation%2Fhuman-values%2Fnature-of-wellbeing-summary.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDepartment%20of%20Conservation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20about%2070%25%20of%20all%20international%20trips%20involve%20some%20%26quot%3Bnature-base%26quot%3B%20activities%2C%20such%20as%20hiking%20or%20visiting%20scenic%20natural%20attractions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20noted%20in%202021%20that%20increased%20tourism%20to%20Milford%20Sound-Piopiotahi%2C%20a%20fjord%20sometimes%20touted%20as%20the%20eighth%20wonder%20of%20the%20world%2C%20put%20it%20under%20%26quot%3Bconsiderable%20stress.%26quot%3B%20Funding%20from%20the%20IVL%20previously%20went%20toward%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.doc.govt.nz%2Fnews%2Fmedia-releases%2F2021-media-releases%2Fnext-step-to-protect-milford-sound-piopiotahi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20master%20plan%20for%20protecting%20it.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-zealand-triples-tourism-entry-fee-to-tackle-environmental-damage-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725359523000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d6da84289b805d1db37a28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-zealand-triples-tourism-entry-fee-to-tackle-environmental-damage-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20October%2C%20New%20Zealand%20will%20triple%20foreign%20tourist%20entry%20fees%20to%20fund%20tourism%20and%20conservation%20efforts%20and%20to%20tackle%20the%20damage%20of%20over-tourism.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzitser%40businessinsider.com%20(Joshua%20Nelken-Zitser)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-zealand-triples-tourism-entry-fee-to-tackle-environmental-damage-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A