t%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20readjustment%20can%20also%20bring%20DINKs%20and%20parent%20friends%20closer%20together.%20Lorimer%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchildfree-but-still-like-kids-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehaving%20so%20many%20friends%20with%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%20(or%20trying%20for%20them)%20exposed%20her%20and%20her%20husband%20to%20conversations%20they%20otherwise%20wouldn't%20have%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20friends%20talking%20about%20fertility%2C%20and%20we%20have%20work%20colleagues%20talking%20about%20infertility%20and%20miscarriages%2C%20which%20are%20just%20life%20experiences%20that%20we%20won't%20ever%20go%20through%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20been%20interesting%20from%20an%20empathy%20perspective.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kushnir%20lives%20far%20from%20her%20childhood%20friends%2C%20she%20still%20keeps%20in%20contact%20with%20them.%20%26quot%3BThey%20ask%20me%20questions%20about%20my%20life%20and%20update%20me%2C%20and%20I%20share%20some%20of%20my%20fears%20about%20having%20a%20family%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20friendships%20also%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20go%20deeper.%20Alexander%20tries%20to%20stay%20open%20to%20all%20new%20connections%2C%20including%20an%20older%20woman%20in%20her%20neighborhood.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20see%20each%20other%2C%20we'll%20sit%20at%20the%20same%20table%20at%20our%20neighborhood%20coffee%20shop%20and%20we'll%20chat%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20DINKS%20like%20Kushnir%20who%20eventually%20want%20to%20become%20parents%2C%20having%20more%20time%20means%20finding%20a%20stronger%20network%20of%20support%20for%20when%20she%20does%20have%20kids.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20go%20through%20being%20pregnant%20and%20having%20a%20kid%20with%20somebody%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20and%20is%20trying%20to%20time%20her%20pregnancy%20with