-think-going-college-worth-it-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eregret%20my%20college%20experience%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20I%20will%20say%20that%20it's%20impacted%20how%20I%20think%20about%20my%20son's.%20More%20than%20anything%2C%20I%20want%20him%20to%20feel%20supported%20no%20matter%20his%20decision%2C%20which%20is%20why%20when%20he%20floated%20the%20idea%20of%20taking%20a%20year%20off%20after%20high%20school%20%E2%80%94%20otherwise%20known%20as%20a%20gap%20year%20%E2%80%94%20I%20didn't%20bat%20an%20eye.%20In%20many%20ways%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20great%20idea.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a1b41ba9-203d-4e30-a8e0-4b1966cd1e0b%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20a%20gap%20year%20is%20(and%20isn't)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-to-career-break-gap-year-resume-gaps-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egap%20year%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20isn't%20just%20a%20random%20break%20that%20students%20who%20aren't%20sure%20what%20they%20want%20to%20do%20after%20high%20school%20take%20%E2%80%94%20when%20approached%20properly%2C%20it's%20a%20span%20of%20time%20(typically%206%20months%20to%20a%20year)%20that%20allows%20a%20young%20adult%20to%20reflect%20on%20what%20they%20really%20want%20from%20life%2C%20and%20where%20they%20want%20to%20go%20literally%2C%20physically%2C%20and%20metaphorically.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYoung%20adults%20can%20use%20the%20time%20to%20expand%20their%20horizons%2C%20travel%20and%20see%20new%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20work%20and%20plan%20for%20their%20future%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e3aa4a54-6166-47df-b9cb-b2d511ea07ea%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20benefits%20to%20taking%20a%20year%20before%20going%20to%20college%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20done%20the%20right%20way%2C%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20