0to%20travel%2C%20and%20he's%20interested%20in%20other%20people%20and%20cultures.%20A%20gap%20year%20could%20help%20him%20nurture%20all%20of%20these%20traits.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20gap%20year%20can%20also%20foster%20more%20independence%2C%20especially%20if%20he%20decides%20to%20move%20out%20of%20his%20dad's%20home%20and%20my%20home%2C%20which%20he%20alternates%20spending%20time%20between%2C%20and%20into%20his%20own%20place.%20It's%20hard%20to%20imagine%20him%20not%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-living-home-challenging-societal-norms-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecoming%20home%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20only%20a%20few%20years%2C%20but%20I%20can%20also%20appreciate%20that%20independence%20could%20be%20something%20he'd%20enjoy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225cb3dba7-06a5-42b9-b730-f8514e4d65a1%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20one%20con%20to%20taking%20a%20gap%20year%20doesn't%20seem%20that%20bad%20to%20me%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20some%2C%20one%20big%2C%20obvious%20con%20for%20a%20gap%20year%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-school-seniors-considering-pandemic-gap-year-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estarting%20college%20a%20year%20later%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20therefore%20graduating%20a%20year%20later%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20every%20student%20graduates%20in%20a%20neat%20four%20years%20to%20begin%20with%2C%20and%20career%20paths%20are%20constantly%20changing%20and%20morphing.%20Also%2C%20as%20someone%20who%20took%20five%20years%20to%20graduate%20from%20college%20(and%20was%20married%20and%20four%20months%20pregnant%20when%20I%20finally%20did)%2C%20I%20can%20say%20that%20the%20extra%20year%20had%20little%20to%20no%20impact%20on%20my%20career%20trajectory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20son%20has%20mentioned%20that%20he%20alre