ons.%20His%20first%20stop%20is%20Brunei%2C%20where%20he%20will%20spend%20two%20days%20and%20meet%20Sultan%20Haji%20Hassanal%20Bolkiah.%20The%20Brunei%20visit%20is%20the%20first-ever%20by%20an%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-to-meet-with-the-sultan-of-brunei-who-boasts-world-s-largest-car-collection-worth-5b-6478680%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topstories%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESultan%20Hassanal%20Bolkiah%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20second-longest%20reigning%20monarch%20in%20the%20world%20after%20the%20late%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20II%2C%20will%20host%20the%20Indian%20PM.%20He%20is%20renowned%20for%20his%20extravagant%20lifestyle%20and%20vast%20wealth.%20With%20an%20estimated%20net%20worth%20of%20around%20%2430%20billion%2C%20he%20was%20once%20recognised%20as%20the%20world's%20richest%20person.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHis%20primary%20home%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-to-meet-brunei-sultan-at-istana-nurul-iman-the-worlds-largest-palace-6478971%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topstories%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIstana%20Nurul%20Iman%20Palace%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20residential%20palace%20according%20to%20the%20Guinness%20Book%20of%20World%20Records.%20Covering%20over%202%2C00%2C000%20square%20metres%2C%20the%20palace%20has%201%2C700%20rooms%2C%20257%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20five%20swimming%20pools.%20The%20palace%20was%20completed%20in%201984%20for%20%241.4%20billion.%20It%20also%20features%20110%20garages.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHassanal%20Bolkiah%20is%20also%20known%20for%20his%20impressive%20car%20collection.%20He%20owns%20over%207%2C000%20vehicles%2C%20including%20600%20Rolls-Royces%2C%20450%20Ferraris%20and%20380%20Bentleys.%20His%20collection%20includes%20rare%20and%20custom-made%20vehicles%20such%20as%20a%20gold-coated%20Rolls-Royce%20and%20a%20Ferrari%20456%20GT%20Venice%2C%20one%20of%20only%20seven%20in%20the%20world.%20This%20collection%20is%20valued%20at%20over%20%245%20billion.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHis%20private%20aviation%20fleet%20is%20equally%20remarkable.%20The%20Sultan%20owns%20a%20Boeing%20747-400%2C%20a%20Boeing%20767-200%2C%20and%20an%20Airbus%20A340-200.%20His%20Boeing%20747-400%2C%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cflying%20palace%2C%E2%80%9D%20is%20lavishly%20decorated%20with%20gold%20and%20Lalique%20crystal.%20The%20aircraft%20is%20said%20to%20have%20cost%20around%20%24400%20million.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHis%20art%20collection%20includes%20significant%20pieces%20like%20Pierre-Auguste%20Renoir's%201892%20masterpiece%20%E2%80%98Young%20Girls%20At%20The%20Piano'%2C%20which%20he%20purchased%20for%20%2470%20million.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnKnown%20for%20his%20extravagant%20personal%20indulgences%2C%20Hassanal%20Bolkiah%20reportedly%20spends%20up%20to%20%2420%2C000%20per%20haircut.%20He%20flies%20his%20favourite%20barber%20from%20London%20to%20Brunei%20for%20grooming%20sessions.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20graduated%20from%20the%20Royal%20Military%20Academy%20Sandhurst%2C%20the%20same%20institution%20attended%20by%20British%20Royals%20Princes%20William%20and%20Harry.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnBeyond%20his%20lavish%20lifestyle%2C%20he%20has%20also%20been%20involved%20in%20various%20charitable%20activities%20and%20governance%20reforms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725355800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fibiab6jo_hassanal-bolkiah_625x300_03_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fall-you-need-to-know-about-sultan-hassanal-bolkiah-and-bruneis-royal-family-6480250%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sultan%20Hassanal%20Bolkiah's%20primary%20home%2C%20the%20Istana%20Nurul%20Iman%20Palace%2C%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20residential%20palace.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fall-you-need-to-k